ğŸ‘ï¸ IR Sensor Wiring (TCRT5000 or KY-033):
IR Sensor Pin	Connects To
VCC	Arduino 5V
GND	Arduino GND
OUT or A0	Arduino A0

Use analog pin A0 to read sensor values via analogRead() in code.

